translation: Thou art Fearless. Thou art Indiscriminate.62.
Thou art the Master of all. Thou art Unborn.
Thou art Countryless. Thou art Garbless.63.
Salutation to Thee O Impenetrable Lord! Salutation to Thee O Unbound Lord! Salutation to Thee O All-Bliss Entity Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Universally-Honoured Lord! Salutation to Thee O All-Treasure Lord! 64.
Salutation to Thee O Masterless Lord! Salutation to Thee O Destroyer Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Unconquerable Lord! Salutation to Thee O Invincible Lord!65.
Salutation to Thee O Deathless Lord! Salutation to Thee O Patronless Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਦੇਸੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਭੇਸੇ ॥੬੬॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Dese|| Namo Sarab Bhese||66||
translation: Salutation to Thee O All-Pervasive Lord! Salutation to Thee O All-garb Lord! 66.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਰਾਜ ਰਾਜੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਾਜ ਸਾਜੇ ॥
transliteration: Namo Raaj Raaje|| Namo Saaj Saaje||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Supreme Sovereign Lord! Salutation to Thee O Best Musical Equipment Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਾਹ ਸਾਹੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਮਾਹ ਮਾਹੇ ॥੬੭॥
transliteration: Namo Shaah Shaahe|| Namo Maah Maahe||67||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Supreme Emporer Lord! Salutation to Thee O Supreme Moon Lord! 67.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਗੀਤ ਗੀਤੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਪ੍ਰੀਤ ਪ੍ਰੀਤੇ ॥
transliteration: Namo Goot Goote|| Namo Proot Proote||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Song Lord! Salutation to Thee O Love Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਰੋਖ ਰੋਖੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸੋਖ ਸੋਖੇ ॥੬੮॥
transliteration: Namo Rokh Rokhe|| Namo Sokh Sokhe||68||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Zeal Lord! Salutation to Thee O Brightest Lord! 68.
